      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey, quick question... im on sertraline for my depression but it doesnt feel like it's doing much lately and finals are coming up so i'm really stressed. i was thinking about adding some st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood naturally. is it okay to take them together or will that be a problem?",
